# Git Workflow (Solo)

```
main → feature/* or fix/* → self-review (bugbot) → PR → squash merge
```

- Never commit or force-push directly to `main`
- Branch naming: `feature/short-name`, `fix/short-name`
- Commits: `git commit -m "type: message"` (PowerShell — no HEREDOC)
- PR: `gh pr create --body-file .github/pr-body-template.md`
- Merge: **squash merge only**

See `docs/git-branch-workflow.md`.
